                    <div class='commenttext'><span class="comment-author"><strong><span style="font-size: 120%;">#18 Kari</span></strong> @ 3:23 pm May 9th, 2008</span><br />
<p>crockpot cooking &#8211; old fashioned Quaker oatmeal, chopped apples, cinnamon, chopped walnuts, etc. into the crockpot at night. Delicious hot breakfast out in the morning. Left overs warm up well later. YUM!</p>
</div>

                    <div class='commenttext'><span class="comment-author"><strong><span style="font-size: 120%;">#19 <a href='http://note.aimeeisdrawing.com' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>Aimee</a></span></strong> @ 3:53 pm May 9th, 2008</span><br />
