                    <div class='commenttext'><span class="comment-author"><strong><span style="font-size: 120%;">#98 <a href='http://bigbadwool.blogspot.com' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>Crystal</a></span></strong> @ 5:59 am May 30th, 2008</span><br />
