                    <div class='commenttext'><span class="comment-author"><strong><span style="font-size: 120%;">#115 <a href='http://debtnewyork.blogspot.com/' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>CL</a></span></strong> @ 3:16 pm July 9th, 2009</span><br />
