                    <div class='commenttext'><span class="comment-author"><strong><span style="font-size: 120%;">#117 liz</span></strong> @ 11:27 am April 17th, 2010</span><br />
<p>This is great for backpacking. Add everything in a freezer ziploc bag. You can just add boiling water, zip up and then eat. Easy clean up and pack out the baggies.</p>
